data.description: Don't miss out on viewing this charming brick home with 2 living rooms and updates that you will love!   New updates include: New LVP Flooring, New paint through out, New fixtures in bathrooms & kitchen, New lighting, New custom built countertops, New ceiling in kitchen.  Enter into the oversized front living room, flow into the open kitchen/dining area, that leads to a spacious family room with fireplace.  An oversized patio adjoining the family room and overlooks the fenced backyard.  Inside you will also find 3 bedrooms each with good sized closets, a full bath with a shower/tub combo and linen closet.  A 2nd linen closet in the hallway and a concenient 1/2 bath off the primary bedroom.  The backyard features a workshop with built-in workbench and cabinets, storage at the back of shop and lean-to on side.  Two concrete driveways at front of property.  This is a great house with a convenient location!  Don't let this one get away!!!
